The following method is intended to remove every negative value from `vals`.

```java
public static void removeNegatives(ArrayList<Integer> vals)
{
    int i = 0;
    while (i < vals.size())
    {
        if (vals.get(i) < 0)
        {
            vals.remove(i);
        }
        else
        {
            i++;
        }
    }
}
```

